INSTALLATION
============

## REQUIREMENTS

To install libopenair you need libcurl and dev tools installed in your
system:
  > sudo apt install build-essential libcurl

## BUILD

 Give following commands:
   > ./configure
   > make
   > sudo make install

## REFRESH DYNAMIC CAHCE

 If you want link it as dynamic library (-l g++ flag), you
 must refresh shared library cache:

   > sudo /sbin/ldconfig -v
